<shuffleanswers>false</shuffleanswers>
<single>true</single>
<answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
A and B are independent.
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
A and B are independent..: Correct
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
A and B are dependent (i.e., not independent).
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
A and B are dependent (i.e.: not independent)…: Incorrect
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Based on the given probabilities, it cannot be concluded with certainty whether A and B are independent or not.
</p>]]></text>
